                         ------------------

           Time Necessary to Produce    Time Necessary  to  Produce
           One Pair of Shoes (Hours)    One Bushel of Wheat (Hours)
       ------------------------------------------------------------
       Jones:                      3                              2
       Smith:                      5                              4
       ------------------------------------------------------------

