       Case 3   Smith       120           0          24             0
                Total       120         120          24            60
       --------------------------------------------------------------

                               TABLE II

                      *    *    *    *    *    *


              TIME NECESSARY TO PRODUCE THE SAME AMOUNT
                 OF GOODS WHILE WORKING ALONE (HOURS)
              -----------------------------------------

                         Jones                            Smith
       --------------------------------------------------------------
       Case 1:     120 +  60 = 180                    200 + 120 = 320
       Case 2:      96 +  90 = 186                    160 + 180 = 340
       Case 3:      72 + 120 = 192                    120 + 240 = 360
       --------------------------------------------------------------

